          %h1 Programs
          %p Each McKinsey Academy program comprises a series of courses that in combination build specific business capabilities for our participants. These programs are based on our experience building capability for our clients, the expertise of McKinsey, as well as our extensive training and development efforts within our firm. Additional programs and courses are under development.
          %p We currently only serve corporate clients, and participants must be sponsored by their companies.
          %p Please email us at <a href="mailto:info@mckinseyacademy.com">info@mckinseyacademy.com</a> for further details.

        %section
          .sub-1 McKinsey Management Program
          %p The McKinsey Management Program (MMP) is a set of courses for rising professionals looking to build leadership and management capabilities. This program integrates perspectives from McKinsey experts and external business leaders from around the globe. <a href="/static/docs/McKA_MMP_Brochure.pdf" target="_blank">View brochure</a>

        %section
          .sub-1 Custom Programs
          %p We offer custom programs that are customized to a single organization’s requirements. McKinsey Academy works with each company to build their program by selecting relevant courses, configuring course content to each company’s context, and tailoring the delivery (e.g., digital, in-person, blended).

        %section
          .sub-1 Unlocking the Potential of Women Program
          %p This six-week digital experience is designed to empower both male and female business leaders to recognize and deliver the full potential of women in the workplace.
          %ul
            %li Improve attraction and retention rates of women
            %li Increase the return on your investment in gender diversity initiatives
            %li Improve performance by empowering your employees
            %li Be a more inclusive and effective leader by getting the most out of your talent
          %p For more information, please email <a href="mailto:women@mckinseyacademy.com">women@mckinseyacademy.com</a> or visit <a href="http://www.mckinsey-upw.com" target="_blank">www.mckinsey-upw.com</a>.

        %section
          .sub-1 Future Business Leaders Forum
          %p McKinsey Academy is convening next-generation leaders from top global companies for a transformational learning journey to achieve peak performance. Participants will develop as inspirational leaders, learn from leading global business and thought leaders, and build a global network of peers. This program provides a mix of digital courses, in-person learning sessions, and live webinars that hone core skills around critical thinking & strategy, innovation & disruption, and leadership & influence.
          %p For more information, please visit <a href="http://www.fblf.info" target="_blank">www.fblf.info</a> or email <a href="mailto:FBLF@mckinseyacademy.com">FBLF@mckinseyacademy.com</a>.

